                    <p>Make your next outing a nautical one!   Plan your event aboard the 73-foot schooner Spirit of Buffalo and enjoy an authentic sailing adventure.  The Spirit of Buffalo can accommodate <!--up to 48 guests--> your guests on a two hour private sail. </p>
                <p>Catering and bar options can be arranged.  Call us at 716.796.7210.  We can help plan and customize your event on the water.</p>
                
                <p>The Spirit of Buffalo is available for Private Charters, Birthday Parties, Bachelor/Bachelorette Parties, Wedding Ceremonies, Wedding Receptions, Company Outings, Retirement Celebrations, Day Sails, Sunset Cruises, Wednesday Wine In The Wind, Private Parties, Pirate Trips, Corporate Functions, Committee Gatherings, Family Reunions, Church Groups, Tour Groups.</p>
                
                <p>Charters are confirmed when Buffalo Sailing Adventures receives your $100 deposit. This non-refundable deposit reserves the function date for your event. All deposits are credited towards payment of your booked event.  </p>
                
